\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces \textsc  {SkillRACE}\xspace  's loop. A run is segmented into episodes and folded into the behavior tree; the tree's branch frontier drives property-guided synthesis of a new input, whose mutated starting-state condition the \emph  {validator} checks \emph  {before} any agent run. Intended branch reach is measured after execution. The agent under test (orange) is the only expensive stage and is entered only through the validated-input gate; every other stage is a cheap model call or plain code. Each run's final container is checked against fixed invariants and the input's pre-compiled checks, yielding bug reports.}}{3}{figure.caption.2}\protected@file@percent }
\providecommand*\caption@xref[2]{\@setref\relax\@undefined{#1}}
\newlabel{fig:pipeline}{{1}{3}{\tool 's loop. A run is segmented into episodes and folded into the behavior tree; the tree's branch frontier drives property-guided synthesis of a new input, whose mutated starting-state condition the \emph {validator} checks \emph {before} any agent run. Intended branch reach is measured after execution. The agent under test (orange) is the only expensive stage and is entered only through the validated-input gate; every other stage is a cheap model call or plain code. Each run's final container is checked against fixed invariants and the input's pre-compiled checks, yielding bug reports}{figure.caption.2}{}}
